<ContentLayout
  title="Wholesale Nicaraguan Green Coffee: Direct Sourcing from El Quetzal, Matagalpa"
  description="Wholesale Nicaraguan green coffee: buy direct from a farm-mill operation, what El Quetzal offers, and how to place your first green coffee order."
  slug="learn/wholesale-nicaraguan-coffee"
  section="learn"
  sectionLabel="For Buyers"
  publishDate="2026-06-23"
